07:43.840 --> 07:52.479
efficient. And that's the quantum part of VQE. But let's talk about reasons why this might not be efficient. One reason

69
07:52.479 --> 07:58.879
for many measurements is to reduce the statistical uncertainty in your estimates for very high precision

